title: Indiana Jones leads police on high-speed chase
text: From elsewhere in New York… Indiana Jones led Yates County police on a high-speed chase Sunday night, landing him in the county lock-up. Yes, really. The (Elmira) Star-Gazette’s Bob Jamieson has more: This Indiana Jones entered the Temple of Zoom and found it led to the Yates County Jail, at least briefly.
